<h2>About Slammin' Sams</h2>
<p>Slammin' Sams is the place to be for delicious food and the latest sports
      <b class="white"> that you can view on the largest High-Def T.V.'s on the coast!</b>.  
      We have two sides from which you can choose, each having its own unique setting.
      <br /> <b class="gold"></b></p>
<h4>Casual Dining</h4>
<p>Our Casual Dining side offers a <span class="white">No Smoking</span> atmosphere 
      with two High-Definition T.V's so you can catch the latest news and sports while you enjoy a nice,
      family dinner.
	  <br /> <a class="menulink" href="http://www.slamminsams.com/menus/casual.html">Casual Dining Menu</a></p>
<h4>Sports Bar &amp; Grill</h4>
<p>Our Sports Bar &amp; Grill side offers a full bar and 4 High-Definition T.V's to catch the latest
      sports events including <span class="white">UFC Fights</span>.  You can also catch all the regular season 
      and post-season games from your favorite sport.  Whether you like college basketball or professional football
      <br /> <a class="menulink" href="http://www.slamminsams.com/menus/sports.html">Sports Bar &amp; Grill Menu</a></p>
<h2>Hours</h2>
<h4>Normal Hours</h4>
